snippet.title: Superhex.io SATISFYING GAMEPLAY! +20K Score! New Design Update
snippet.description:
Play Superhex.io: http://superhex.io/
Video by: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVzIwnCFwlMQoUuw87TqAeQ

Your goal? Conquer as much territory as possible, don't get hit, defend your land and try to find the best strategy to conquer all the map, but be careful ennemies won't let you do so.

Songs from:
https://www.youtube.com/user/FreeSongsToUse
